sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User
    participant Workbench as Workbench
    participant Manifest as codex-bridge.yaml
    participant Standard as workbench-sdd/v1
    participant Indexes as .sdd indexes
    participant Indexer as SDD Indexer
    participant Pack as Context Pack Engine
    participant LLM as Codex or LLM
    participant Files as Selected project files

    User->>Workbench: Request action, e.g. new feature
    Workbench->>Manifest: Read project adoption config
    Manifest-->>Workbench: Standard version, roots, domains, policies
    Workbench->>Standard: Resolve standard rules
    Standard-->>Workbench: Artifact, diagram, traceability, and LLM rules
    Workbench->>Indexes: Read generated indexes
    alt indexes fresh
        Indexes-->>Workbench: Candidate specs, diagrams, modules, domains
    else indexes missing or stale
        Workbench->>Indexer: Regenerate indexes from manifest and SDD roots
        alt regeneration succeeds
            Indexer-->>Workbench: index_status=regenerated plus candidates
        else regeneration fails
            Indexer-->>Workbench: index_status=failed plus next action
            Workbench->>Workbench: Record degraded or blocked context state
        end
    end
    Workbench->>Pack: Build action-specific context pack
    Pack-->>Workbench: Required files, candidates, limits, blocked reads, index status
    Workbench->>LLM: Send prompt with context pack and rules
    LLM->>Files: Read only selected files
    Files-->>LLM: Minimal relevant context
    LLM-->>Workbench: Proposed SDD or implementation action
